headline: Salute the Troops Announces October Vetrepreneur Project Cohort with $8,500 in Awards for Veteran Business Owners
summary: Salute the Troops, in partnership with the Wisconsin Veterans Chamber of Commerce (WVCC) and The Venture Project, will host its next Vetrepreneur Project cohort October 24–26, 2025, at Chula Vista Resort in Wisconsin Dells. The three-day program will feature training, mentorship, and a live pitch contest awarding $8,500 in total prizes — including awards of $5,000, $2,500, and $1,000.
